# Streaming Workflow Results

- Streams incremental tool output and step results in real time.
- Handles different chunk types via a `switch` statement.

```ts
const run = await workflow.createRunAsync();
const stream = await run.stream({ inputData });

for await (const chunk of stream) {
  switch (chunk.type) {
    case 'tool-call-delta':
      process.stdout.write(chunk.argsTextDelta);
      break;
    case 'step-result':
      console.log(`Done: ${chunk.payload.status}`);
      break;
  }
}
```

