# RuntimeContext Sharing

- Stores arbitrary key/value pairs (e.g., `apiKey`, `userTier`).
- Makes them available inside steps via `runtimeContext.get()`.

```ts
const ctx = new RuntimeContext();
ctx.set("apiKey", process.env.API_KEY);
ctx.set("userTier", "premium");

await run.start({ 
  inputData, 
  runtimeContext: ctx 
});

// In step
execute: async ({ runtimeContext }) => {
  const apiKey = runtimeContext.get("apiKey");
}
```

