# Tool as Workflow Step

- Wraps an existing tool (`weatherTool`) with `createStep()`.
- Maps static input (`city: "London"`) before invoking the step.

```ts
const weatherStep = createStep(weatherTool);

const workflow = createWorkflow({ ... })
  .map({ city: "London" })
  .then(weatherStep)
  .commit();
```

