# Parallel Processing

- Executes multiple data-fetching steps concurrently.
- Combines the results in a final aggregation step.

```ts
const workflow = createWorkflow({ ... })
  .parallel([
    fetchUserStep,
    fetchOrdersStep,
    fetchPreferencesStep
  ])
  .then(combineDataStep)
  .commit();
```

