# Dynamic Workflow Execution

- Invokes another workflow (`order-flow`) inside a tool.
- Returns the status from the nested workflow run.

```ts
const processOrderTool = createTool({
  execute: async ({ context, mastra }) => {
    const workflow = mastra.getWorkflow("order-flow");
    const run = await workflow.createRunAsync();
    
    const result = await run.start({
      inputData: { orderId: context.orderId }
    });
    
    return { status: result.result.status };
  }
});
```